 EVEN ladies who are not fashionable know that the shirt dress is a must-have. You can’t afford not to have one in your wardrobe.      They are an important part of a woman’s outfit. With a well-designed and quality shirt dress, you can look good and smart for any occasion. It is great for any day of the week.         They come in a variety of fabrics and designs. They have great versatility and they are one fashion item that has remained constant and are likely to remain like that for ages to come. They are a wardrobe staple and their artworks are of different varieties, styles and colours.    You can’t go wrong with a shirt dress when you want to be comfortable. Along with accompanying accessories, it can determine just how hot a lady looks .    